==English==
===Adverbal phrase===
'''in the long run'''

#{{idiom}} After a very long time; [[eventually]]; over a long period of time; more generally.
#:''It may cost a bit more [[up front]], but I think you will find that it is a sturdier product '''in the long run'''.''

====Translations====
*Dutch: [[op termijn]], [[uiteindelijk]]
*Finnish: [[ajan pitkään]], [[ajan oloon]], [[ajan mittaan]]
*French: [[à terme]]
*Swedish: [[i långa loppet]]